        "subject": "❌ VPN Connection Failed",
        "html": "<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background: #e74c3c; color: white;\">\n  <h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">❌ VPN Connection Failed</h1>\n  \n  <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0;\">\n    <p><strong>Attempted Country:</strong> {{$node[\"Select VPN Server\"].json[\"country\"]}}</p>\n    <p><strong>Server:</strong> {{$node[\"Select VPN Server\"].json[\"server\"]}}</p>\n    <p><strong>Current IP:</strong> {{$json[\"ip\"]}}</p>\n    <p><strong>Current Location:</strong> {{$json[\"city\"]}}, {{$json[\"country_name\"]}}</p>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0;\">\n    <h3>🔧 Troubleshooting Steps</h3>\n    <ol>\n      <li>Check VPN service status</li>\n      <li>Try a different server</li>\n      <li>Restart VPN client</li>\n      <li>Check internet connection</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n  \n  <p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;\">Please try again or contact support.</p>\n</div>",
